## ğŸ’¡ Tips
- Donâ€™t pronounce final *t* or *s* in most numbers (e.g. *deux*, *trois*).  
- Hyphens connect all parts from 17 upward (*vingt-trois, trente-cinq*).  
- French numbers use a **space** instead of a comma for thousands â†’ *1 500*, not *1,500*.  

